  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after about eight days-- I don't remember exactly-- eight days or nine days, we arrived in Rowne, which is R-O-W-N-E, a place, a town, in Eastern Poland, in Wolyn, where my cousin of my father, Witek Stok or Witold Stok, had a factory similar to the factory of my grandfather in Warsaw, a soap factory.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was well-known locally because he was the local capitalist, so to say.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they lived in a nice villa, in a very nice house in the middle of quite large fruit orchard, garden.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Otherwise, Rowne, I remember, was an Eastern European town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was, of course, much smaller.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The houses were single-story or two-story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was all together, of course, much more behind, so to say, in comparison to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came, we moved into the-- we moved into the villa of Witek.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Witek and his wife, they had no children and the house was quite big, so they accommodated all of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think all nine of us, yes, in the beginning, at least.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure what happened later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then immediately on the day when we came or maybe one day later, there was an absolutely horrific bombardment, by the Germans, which was one of the worst.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Luckily they drug trenches in the garden and we were hiding in those trenches, although they were not properly protected, but one heard bombs falling nearby and the noise of the-- of the anti-aircraft machine guns.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was-- and then there was a general pandemonium and people were screaming and shouting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a really terrible experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after maybe 40 minutes, when we got out of those trenches there, I remember that the whole street was opposite nearby, everything was burning.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
